 143:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****      [..]
 144:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****      (#) Start or Stop simple timers
 145:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****               (++)Simple time base: HAL_HRTIM_SimpleBaseStart(),HAL_HRTIM_SimpleBaseStop(),
