 272:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****      The compilation flag USE_HAL_HRTIM_REGISTER_CALLBACKS when set to 1
 273:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****      allows the user to configure dynamically the driver callbacks.
