 278:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****      Function HAL_HRTIM_RegisterCallback() allows to register following callbacks:
 279:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****        (+) Fault1Callback               : Fault 1 interrupt callback function
 280:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****        (+) Fault2Callback               : Fault 2 interrupt callback function
