 283:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****        (+) Fault5Callback               : Fault 5 interrupt callback function
 284:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****        (+) SystemFaultCallback          : System fault interrupt callback function
 285:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****        (+) BurstModePeriodCallback      : Burst mode period interrupt callback function
 286:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****        (+) SynchronizationEventCallback : Sync Input interrupt callback function
