1154:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****     [..]  This section provides functions allowing to:
1155:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Configure simple output channel
1156:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple output compare
1157:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple output compare
1158:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple output compare and enable interrupt
1159:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple output compare and disable interrupt
1160:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple output compare and enable DMA transfer
1161:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple output compare and disable DMA transfer
1162:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****        -@- When a HRTIM timer operates in simple output compare mode
1163:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****            the output level is set to a programmable value when a match
1164:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****            is found between the compare register and the counter.
1165:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****            Compare unit 1 is automatically associated to output 1
1166:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****            Compare unit 2 is automatically associated to output 2
1167:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c **** @endverbatim
