1770:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  ===============================================================================
1771:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****     [..]  This section provides functions allowing to:
1772:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Configure simple PWM output channel
1773:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple PWM output
1774:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple PWM output
1775:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple PWM output and enable interrupt
1776:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple PWM output and disable interrupt
1777:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple PWM output and enable DMA transfer
1778:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple PWM output and disable DMA transfer
1779:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       -@- When a HRTIM timer operates in simple PWM output mode
1780:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           the output level is set to a programmable value when a match is
1781:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           found between the compare register and the counter and reset when
1782:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           the timer period is reached. Duty cycle is determined by the
1783:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           comparison value.
1784:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           Compare unit 1 is automatically associated to output 1
1785:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           Compare unit 2 is automatically associated to output 2
1786:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c **** @endverbatim
