6388:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *  @brief  Functions called when HRTIM generates an interrupt
6389:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *          7 interrupts can be generated by the master timer:
6390:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Master timer registers update
6391:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Synchronization event received
6392:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Master timer repetition event
6393:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Master Compare 1 to 4 event
6394:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *          14 interrupts can be generated by each timing unit:
6395:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Delayed protection triggered
6396:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Counter reset or roll-over event
6397:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Output 1 and output 2 reset (transition active to inactive)
6398:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Output 1 and output 2 set (transition inactive to active)
6399:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Capture 1 and 2 events
6400:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Timing unit registers update
6401:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Repetition event
6402:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Compare 1 to 4 event
6403:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *          7 global interrupts are generated for the whole HRTIM:
6404:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - System fault and Fault 1 to 5 (regardless of the timing unit attribution)
6405:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Burst mode period completed
